		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:20px;color:#222222">
			
			<table width="550" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tbody><tr>
			
			<td align="left" valign="top"><a href="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/photos/ncstc_staff-sideimg-actv2_211014.jpg" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/photos/ncstc_staff-sideimg-actv2_211014.jpg" alt="" width="250" height="300" border="0"></a></td>
			
			<td align="left" valign="top"><p>The Challenge is the UK's largest provider of National Citizen Service (NCS) - an exciting youth and community programme devoted to strengthening ties in local communities and helping 15-17 year-olds to grow in confidence and skills.</p>
			
			<p>In 2014, around 20% of our paid summer staff were teachers, who brought their experience and enthusiasm to the NCS programme. If you're interested in youth work, facilitation or social care a role with The Challenge is for you!</p></td>
			
			
			</tr></tbody></table>

		</td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="600" height="50" colspan="3" align="center" valign="top"></td>

		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:18px;line-height:22px;color:#010101"><strong>OUR SEASONAL ROLES</strong></td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="center" valign="top"><img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/staffing/Images/ncstc_hr_290914.jpg" width="550" height="22" border="0" style="display:block"></td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:20px;color:#222222"><p>The Challenge is dedicated to providing NCS to as many young people as possible, regardless of their background and ability. We are recruiting <strong>Support Workers</strong> and <strong>Personal Coaches</strong> to help us ensure that all of our young people can take part to their full potential.</p> 

<p>These roles provide one-to-one support to a young person with additional requirements or challenging behaviour, and require a patient, enthusiastic and experienced individual. Experience of working with young people with challenging behaviour and/or additional requirements is essential for these intense and rewarding roles.</p>
		
		<p>We also have exciting and challenging roles to suit your experience in youth work, social care and teaching. Work as a <strong>Leader</strong> and guide 60-84 young people through the programme, or take on one of our <strong>Mentor</strong> roles, facilitating sessions and pastorally caring for a small team. Showcase and share your music, film, photography, sport, drama or enterprise skills as a <strong>Practitioner</strong>. Wherever your skills lie, we have a great role for you!</p>
		
		<p>Further information on our seasonal roles, including full role descriptions, can be found at <strong>ncsthechallenge.org/seasonal-roles</strong>.</p></td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="600" height="50" colspan="3" align="center" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		
